  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will compare hypertension treatment pattern of stroke patients with non-stroke
      patients receiving medical care from outpatient clinics at neurology specialty centers in
      Korea. It will evaluate target BP achievement rate in patients with stroke compared to
      patients without stroke and investigate factors affecting BP target goal efficacy in these
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
